---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { MENU_ITEMS } from '../utils/constants';
---

<Layout title="菜单介绍" description="探索虾姑猪脚姜的招牌菜单：沙姜猪脚（肉质脆爽、沙姜香气浓郁）与猪脚姜（甜中带辣、胶质丰富），两大粤式猪脚经典做法。">
  <fragment slot="header"><Header /></fragment>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-text-primary via-secondary-dark to-text-primary overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #D4A04A 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-heading text-white text-shadow-lg mb-4">菜单介绍</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-background-alt/80">一店双味 · 两大粤式猪脚经典做法</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sha Jiang Pig Foot Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-background-alt to-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg order-1">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <span class="text-7xl">🥩</span>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mt-4">沙姜猪脚 — 胶质Q弹</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-2">
          <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-1">Signature Cold Dish</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-2">沙姜猪脚</h2>
          <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-primary mb-6"></div>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-text-primary">沙姜猪脚</strong> 是店内最具人气的招牌菜之一。
              沙姜（又称山奈）的独特辛香，与猪脚的胶质Q弹完美融合，是一道令人回味无穷的粤式凉菜。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Details -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">👅</span> 口感特色
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">肉质脆爽、Q弹紧致，每一口都能感受到猪脚的胶质与弹性，令人回味无穷。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">🌿</span> 风味亮点
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">沙姜香气浓郁，辛香与鲜味完美融合。沙姜碎爆香后混合生抽、白糖、高汤，层次丰富。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">⚙️</span> 制作工序
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-1">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
              焯水去腥
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
              高压炖煮至软嫩
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
              冰水浸泡使肉质紧致
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
              沙姜碎爆香调味
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Cultural Note -->
      <div class="bg-background-alt rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3">📖 文化意涵</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          猪脚在粤式饮食文化中象征「发财就手」，是广东年夜饭中不可或缺的传统菜肴。
          沙姜猪脚作为粤式凉菜的代表，将这份吉祥寓意与清爽口感完美结合，
          既是日常美食，也是节日餐桌上的亮点。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ginger Vinegar Pig Foot Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-background-alt">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-1">Traditional Comfort Food</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-2">猪脚姜</h2>
          <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-primary mb-6"></div>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-text-primary">猪脚姜</strong> 是粤式传统滋补美食的代表，
              以猪脚、老姜、鸡蛋和甜醋慢火焖煮而成。甜中带辣、胶质丰富，
              既是产妇坐月子的传统补品，也是冬季暖身的街头美食。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <span class="text-7xl">🍲</span>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mt-4">猪脚姜 — 瓦煲焖煮</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Details -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">👅</span> 口感特色
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">甜中带辣，胶质丰富。焖煮至软嫩的猪脚吸收甜醋的精华，入口即化，暖胃又满足。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">🌿</span> 食材与工序
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">选用老姜切厚片炒香，猪脚焯水后与甜醋、鸡蛋一同放入瓦煲，慢火焖煮至入味。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">💪</span> 功效说明
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-1">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span>
              开胃提神
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span>
              补血补钙
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span>
              养颜美肤
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0"></span>
              驱寒暖身
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Cultural Note -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-md border border-background-alt">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-3">📖 文化意涵</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
          猪脚姜是广东产妇坐月子的传统补品，被认为有驱风散寒、补充胶质之效。
          随著时代演变，这道充满温暖记忆的美食已成为广东人冬季餐桌上的常见菜肴，
          甚至衍生出「猪脚姜配饭」的街头美食文化，深受男女老少的喜爱。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-background text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading text-text-primary mb-4">
        想品尝最道地的粤式猪脚美味？
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">
        欢迎来店或致电预订，体验沙姜猪脚的Q弹与猪脚姜的温润
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-text-primary font-bold rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg">
          联络我们
        </a>
        <a href="tel:18688647083" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg">
          立即致电 186-8864-7083
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <fragment slot="footer"><Footer /></fragment>
</Layout>
